Paper: hep-th/9501026

Date: 1995-01-10

Title: The Heat Kernel Coefficients to the Matrix Schr\"odinger Operator

Authors: I. G. Avramidi and R. Schimming

Comments: 16 pages, Plain TeX, 33 KB, no figures

Journal-ref: J.Math.Phys. 36 (1995) 5042-5054

The heat kernel coefficients $H_k$ to the Schr\"odinger operator with amatrix potential are investigated. We present algorithms and explicitexpressions for the Taylor coefficients of the $H_k$. Special terms arediscussed, and for the one-dimensional case some improved algorithms arederived.